1. Information We Do Not Collect
Infinite Fact does not require users to create an account, log in, or provide personal information. We do not directly collect personal data such as name, email address, phone number, or location.

2. Advertising
Our app uses Google AdMob, a third-party advertising service, to display advertisements.
AdMob may collect and use certain information automatically, including:
  Advertising ID
  Device information
  Interaction data with advertisements

This information is used to provide and improve advertising services.

We display child-appropriate advertisements in compliance with the Google Play Families Policy where applicable.

You can learn more about how Google uses data here:
https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads

